,\\\"text\\\":\\\"A nossa equipa cria o conteúdo completo — copywriting e design de posts e stories. Enviamos para aprovação antes de publicar. Podes ter tão pouco ou tanto envolvimento quanto quiseres.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Quanto devo investir em Google Ads?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"O orçamento mínimo recomendado para Google Ads em Portugal é €300–€500/mês em adspend (separado da nossa fee de gestão). Abaixo deste valor os dados são insuficientes para otimizar bem as campanhas.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Como medem o retorno do investimento?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Configuramos rastreio de conversões desde o primeiro dia — chamadas, formulários, compras ou qualquer ação relevante para o teu negócio. O relatório mensal mostra custo por lead/venda e ROI calculado com dados reais, não estimativas.\\\"}}]}\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"12:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"svc-page\\\",\\\"data-color\\\":\\\"yellow\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L1c\\\",null,{\\\"color\\\":\\\"yellow\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L4\\\",null,{\\\"id\\\":\\\"ld-svc-marketing-digital\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"strategy\\\":\\\"afterInteractive\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"@context\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://schema.org\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Service\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"@id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://elementgroup.pt/servicos/marketing-digital#service\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Marketing Digital\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Gestão de redes sociais, Google Ads e SEO mensal para PMEs em Portugal. Instagram, Facebook e Google geridos por especialistas. Relatórios mensais. Desde 350€/mês.\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"url\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://elementgroup.pt/servicos/marketing-digital\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"provider\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\"@type\