nto quiseres.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Quanto devo investir em Google Ads?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"O orçamento mínimo recomendado para Google Ads em Portugal é €300–€500/mês em adspend (separado da nossa fee de gestão). Abaixo deste valor os dados são insuficientes para otimizar bem as campanhas.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Como medem o retorno do investimento?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Configuramos rastreio de conversões desde o primeiro dia — chamadas, formulários, compras ou qualquer ação relevante para o teu negócio. O relatório mensal mostra custo por lead/venda e ROI calculado com dados reais, não estimativas.\"}}]}12:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"svc-page\",\"data-color\":\"yellow\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L1c\",null,{\"color\":\"yellow\"}],[\"$\",\"$L4\",null,{\"id\":\"ld-svc-marketing-digital\",\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"strategy\":\"afterInteractive\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Service\\\",\\\"@id\\\":\\\"https://elementgroup.pt/servicos/marketing-digital#service\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Marketing Digital\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Gestão de redes sociais, Google Ads e SEO mensal para PMEs em Portugal. Instagram, Facebook e Google geridos por especialistas. Relatórios mensais. Desde 350€/mês.\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://elementgroup.pt/servicos/marketing-digital\\\",\\\"provider\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ProfessionalService\\\",\\\"@id\\\":\\\"https://elementgroup.pt/#organization\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Element Group\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://elementgroup.pt\\\"},\\\"areaServed\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Country\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Portugal\\\"},\\\"offers\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Offer\\\",\\\"price\\\":350,\\\"priceCurrency\\\":\\\"EUR\\\",\\\"availability\\\":\\\"https://schema.org/InStock\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://elementgroup.pt/servicos/marketing-digital\\\"},\\\"image\\\":\\\"https://e